meta.response.choices.0.text: I am. And the fact that there is a physical world out there to which our senses give us access is not a matter of opinion or theory, but a truth about the facts of the universe. A fact is a truth about the universe. C. On Credulity I will now offer a short list of what I can see as the most important ideas concerning the mind in the tradition.
